<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You for Your Booking!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f7f8f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #0c6596;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .thank-you-message {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #1e86b6;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .images-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .images-container img {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #0c6596;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-top: 30px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Thank You for Your Booking!</h1>
        
        <div class="thank-you-message">
            <p>Your booking has been successfully confirmed. We appreciate your choice to travel with us!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="images-container">
            <img src="images/Airplane Image.jpg" alt="Airplane Image">
            <img src="images/Screenshot (188).png" alt="Thank You Image">
            <img src="images/open_graph_default_image.jpg" alt="Flight Image">
        </div>

        <p>If you have any questions about your booking, feel free to <strong>contact us</strong>.</p>

        <a href="/home" class="button">Go to Home</a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
